&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Due to the nature of healthcare services provided to our customers, partners and members, all work must be provided in the U.S. Data, specifically personal health information may not be accessed, disclosed or used outside of the U.S. Please note that the U.S. is limited to the 50 states of the United States -- it does not include U.S. territories like Puerto Rico.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
